quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  65,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  65,1,ae paighambar ( musalmanoon se keh do ke ) jab tum aurton ko Talaq dainay lagu to adt ke shuru mein Talaq do aur adt ka shumaar rakho. aur khuda se jo tumhara perwar-digaar hai daro. ( nah to tum hi ) un ko ( ayyaam adt mein ) un ke gharon se nikalu aur nah woh ( khud hi ) nikleen. haan agar woh Sarih be hiyai karen ( to nikaal dena chahiye ) aur yeh khuda ki hade hain. jo khuda ki hado se tajawaz kere ga woh apne aap par zulm kere ga. ( ae Talaq dainay walay ) tujhekiya maloom shayad khuda is ke baad koi ( rajat ki ) Sabeel peda kardey
  65,2,phir jab woh apni meyaad ( yani aintaqaza-ay iddat ) ke qareeb pohnch jayen to ya to un ko achi terhan ( zojiat mein ) rehne do ya achi terhan se alehda kardo aur apne mein se do munhsif mardon ko gawah karlo aur ( gawah ho! ) khuda ke liye durust gawahi dena. un baton se is shakhs ko nasiyaat ki jati hai jo khuda par aur roz akhirat par imaan rakhta hai. aur jo koi khuda se daray ga woh is ke liye ( ranj-o-mehan se ) mukhlasi ( ki soorat ) peda kere ga
  65,3,aur is ko aisi jagah se rizaq day ga jahan se ( vahm o ) gumaan bhi nah ho. aur jo khuda par bharosa rakhay ga to woh is ko kifayat kere ga. khuda apne kaam ko ( jo woh karna chahta hai ) poora kardaita hai. khuda ne har cheez ka andaza muqarrar kar rakha hai
  65,4,aur tumhari ( mutalqa ) aurtain jo haiz se na umeed hochuki hon agar tum ko ( un ki adt ke baray mein ) shuba ho to un ki adt teen mahinay hai aur jin ko abhi haiz nahi anay laga ( un ki adt bhi yahi hai ) aur hamal wali aurton ki adt waza hamal ( yani bchch_h jan'nay ) taq hai. aur jo khuda se daray ga khuda is ke kaam mein sahoolat peda kardey ga
  65,5,yeh khuda ke hukum hain jo khuda ne tum par nazil kiye hain. aur jo khuda se daray ga woh is se is ke gunah daur kar day ga aur usay ajar azeem bakhshay ga
  65,6,aurton ko ( ayyaam adt mein ) apne Maqdoor ke mutabiq wahein rakho jahan khud rehtay ho aur un ko tang karne ke liye takleef nah do aur agar hamal se hon to bchch_h jan'nay taq un ka kharch dete raho. phir agar woh bachay ko tumahray kehnay se doodh pilain to un ko un ki ujrat do. aur ( bachay ke baray mein ) pasandeeda tareeq se mwaqft rakho. aur agar baahum zid ( aur na-itefaqi ) karo ge to ( bachay ko ) is ke ( baap ke ) kehnay se koi aur aurat doodh pilaaye gi
  65,7,sahib wusat ko apni wusat ke mutabiq kharch karna chahiye. aur jis ke rizaq mein tangi ho woh jitna khuda ne is ko diya hai is ke mawafiq kharch kere. khuda kisi ko takleef nahi deta magar isi ke mutabiq jo is ko diya hai. aur khuda anqareeb tangi ke baad kashaish bakhshay ga
  65,8,aur bohat si bustiyon ( ke rehne walon ) ne apne perwar-digaar aur is ke payghambaroon ke ehkaam se sar kashi ki to hum ne un ko sakht hisaab mein pakar liya aur un par ( aisa ) azaab nazilkiya jo nah dekha tha nah suna
  65,9,so unhon ne apne kamon ki saza ka maza chakh liya aur un ka injaam nuqsaan hi to tha
  65,10,khuda ne un ke liye sakht azaab tayyar kar rakha hai. to ae arbab Danish jo imaan laaye ho khuda se daro. khuda ne tumahray paas nasiyaat ( ki kitaab ) bhaije hai
  65,11,( aur apne ) paighambar ( bhi beje hain ) jo tumahray samnay khuda ki wazeh المطالب ayatain parhte hain taakay jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay hain un ko andheray se nikaal kar roshni mein le ayen aur jo shakhs imaan laaye ga aur amal naik kere ga un ko baghaye bahisht mein daakhil kere ga jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahen hain abadd الاآباد un mein rahen ge. khuda ne un ko khoob rizaq diya hai
  65,12,khuda hi to hai jis ne saat aasman peda kiye aur aisi hi zameenen. un mein ( khuda ke ) hukum utarte rehtay hain taakay tum log jaan lau ke khuda cheez par Qadir hai. aur yeh ke khuda apne ilm se har cheez par ihata kiye hue hai
